text: "Procabacteriaceae" is a Candidatus family of uncultivated Gram-negative Betaproteobacteria. The sole genus, "Procabacter", was identified as an obligate endosymbiont of Acanthamoeba. ==References== ==External links== * Procabacteriaceae List of Prokaryotic Names with Standing in Nomenclature Category:Betaproteobacteria Category:Candidatus taxa
